snippet: Victor Dubuisson charged into a five-shot lead at the Turkish Airlines Open in Antalya by shooting a nine-under-par 63, and Raphael Jacquelin shot a course-record 62.
lead_paragraph: Victor Dubuisson charged into a five-shot lead at the Turkish Airlines Open in Antalya by shooting a nine-under-par 63, and Raphael Jacquelin shot a course-record 62.

headline.main: One Frenchman Leads; Another Ties a Tour Record
